AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner (ACCP) Exam Notes (2026 Full Update)

These are notes regarding the ACCP exam which were gradually completed while studying the exam objectives, now fully updated for the CLF-C02 standards.

Who should take this exam?



The AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner (CLF-C02) exam is intended for individuals



who can effectively demonstrate an overall knowledge of the AWS Cloud



independent of a specific job role.

You can find every updated information in this link which is the official and reputable information.

The following table lists the main content domains and their weightings.



